quote: I saw the Eagle Tree for the first time on the third Monday of the month of March, which I guess could be considered auspicious if I believed in magic or superstition or religion...
quote_letters: I SAW THE EAGLE TREE FOR THE FIRST TIME ON THE THIRD MONDAY OF THE MONTH OF MARCH WHICH I GUESS COULD BE CONSIDERED AUSPICIOUS IF I BELIEVED IN MAGIC OR SUPERSTITION OR RELIGION
